               <H2>Market Summary</H2>
               <p>Laurentian Hills Plaza is a grocery anchored, neighbourhood center in Kitchener Ontario. The center has a strong mix of destination tenants and enjoys excellent access and visibility from Westmount Road, a major arterial route with a vehicular traffic count exceeding 20,000/ day. The City of Kitchener has one of the lowest unemployment rates in the province, while often experiencing some of the highest population growth rates in the country.</p>
               <br>
               <strong>Total GLA:  </strong>80,203 square feet	<br><br>
               
               
              
         
          
